nonmem2rx 0.1.0
  • Reference

    Read a nonmem xml and create output similar to the `nmlst()`

    nmxml.Rd

    Read a nonmem xml and create output similar to the `nmlst()`

    nmxml(xml)

    Arguments

    xml

    xml file

    Value

    list of nonmem information

    Author

    Matthew L. Fidler

    Examples

    nmxml(system.file("mods/cpt/runODE032.xml", package="nonmem2rx"))
